{"tid":1784203,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃明志演唱會俾馬拉政府搞 冇人提？","createTime":"2019-12-15T13:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T09:37:08.000Z","uid":262346,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"122240d2dfca2b0c349276dc5312efa7c1f07c0b","tid":1784203,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:26:40.000Z","msg":"黃明志係12月31搞跨年演唱會<br />\n點知俾仆街馬拉政府諸多阻撓<br />\n<br />\n本身09年黃明志為馬拉少數族裔發聲<br />\n已經俾馬來人批鬥同政府封殺<br />\n之後避走台灣發展<br />\n<br />\n好不容易今年先係馬拉再搞演唱會<br />\n<br />\n但又因為拍片讀出 <br />\n政府機關批准搞演唱會既潛規則<br />\n而再度被逼停辦<br />\n<br />\n我好中意黃明志<br />\n佢唱過首廣東話去欣賞香港文化<br />\n<br />\n可否connect 埋黃明志<br />\n同埋不滿馬拉政府既人<br />\n<br />\n搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3417e8e2dc40f1cd443c7b9372fe942cc035af4c","tid":1784203,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:27:29.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"734fcf1fea1be422413ebea03f3850cb3ee3a27a","tid":1784203,"uid":129466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都好鍾意佢"},{"pid":"084a10b460968ac47fae79763694382048b5966c","tid":1784203,"uid":115982,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:27:57.000Z","msg":"佢奶共喎"},{"pid":"47dce27875a9b3c58c4f4975b6e1c857570d5cf4","tid":1784203,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:28:24.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">德國戰線要人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://